Feature: Work Request Submission Form

  As an administrator
  I want to have access to view all Work Request Form submissions and configure who gets email notifications when a user submits a new Work Request Form
  So that I may properly manage and delegate management of these form submissions

  As an administrator
  I want to receive email notifications when users submit Work Request Forms
  So that I may contact these users for follow-up

  As a guest user
  I want to fill out a form describing my training center details
  So that I may have my information sent to sales representatives who may contact me in the future

  As a registered user
  I want to fill out a form describing my training center details
  So that I may have my information sent to sales representatives who may contact me in the future

